<Paragraph>
Hierarchy Navigator helps to navigate forward or backward to the desired path. This sample showcases the important capabilities of Hierarchy Navigator control.
</Paragraph>
<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>The visual styles denote built-in themes, including metro, office themes, visual studio, etc.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Edit mode helps to navigate to the desired location by entering the path details physically.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>History helps to show the recently explored path.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Progress helps to show the ongoing work. Cancellation of progress is also possible.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>
